developer_response.body:
theres no bug involved for sure, multiple people have made it past the tutorial
make sure you're putting the weapon in the correct inventory spot, like pistols go on the right and left pocket (positioned like real pockets) while ars go on your back (over your shoulder), and not the ones on your vest, as they are for projectiles (later in the tutorial).
if you still need help, join the discord and contact one of the owners (and if you want to talk to the one writing this response, contact specifically the dev, shadowflame45)
